product.title: Fresh Chinigura Rice
product.description: rice, (Oryza sativa), edible starchy cereal grain and the grass plant (family Poaceae) by which it is produced. ... Rice is cooked by boiling, or it can be ground into a flour. It is eaten alone and in a great variety of soups, side dishes, and main dishes in Asian, Middle Eastern, and many other cuisines.
